Package: dan-glasses-daemons
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-flask, python3-requests, python3-yaml, python3-numpy, python3-aiohttp, python3-websockets
Recommends: python3-sentence-transformers, python3-pillow, python3-opencv
Description: Dan Glasses daemon services
 Six HTTP daemons that form the runtime backbone of the Dan Glasses wearable
 AI assistant: audiod (VAD+STT), perceptiond (camera+VLM), memoryd (semantic
 memory), toold (sandboxed tool execution), ttsd (text-to-speech), and
 os-toold (OS-level guard). All six ship as systemd units and bind to
 loopback by default. The OpenClaw gateway is configured separately via
 /etc/openclaw/openclaw.json and is NOT part of this package.
